name: EightStatesData
ddl:
CREATE TABLE "EightStatesData" (
    "State" varchar(30)   NOT NULL,
    "State_Abbreviation" varchar(30)   NOT NULL,
    "Year" Int   NOT NULL,
    "Gender" varchar(30)   NOT NULL,
    "EduLevel" varchar(30)   NOT NULL,
    "EduLevelCode" Int   NOT NULL,
    "Births" Int   NOT NULL,
    "AvgMotherAge" Float   NOT NULL,
    "AvgBirthWeight" Float   NOT NULL
);
